SELECT d.community_name, t.target_population, t.assistance_program, p.start_date, p.end_date FROM target_communities t JOIN program_history p ON t.community_id = p.community_id JOIN demographic_data d ON t.community_id = d.id WHERE p.start_date >= '2022-01-01' AND p.end_date <= '2022-12-31';
SELECT d.community_name, d.population, d.median_income, t.target_population FROM demographic_data d JOIN target_communities t ON d.id = t.community_id WHERE d.population BETWEEN 10000 AND 50000;
